		<link>https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/some-facts-about-call-centers.html</link>
				<comments>https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/some-facts-about-call-centers.html#respond</comments>
				<pubDate>Mon, 06 Feb 2012 07:18:40 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Alicia Johnson]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[virtual call center]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[call center outsourcing]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/?p=4467</guid>
				<description><![CDATA[Call centers are basically centralized offices created for the sake of taking and relaying a huge quantity of calls. A virtual call center is generally run by a specific company for administering incoming service or product supports as well as information requests from the customers. Outgoing phone calls for the purpose of telemarketing and debt [&#8230;]]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a rel="&quot;lightbox&quot;&quot;" href="http://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/virtual-call-center.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-4468" title="virtual call center" src="http://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/virtual-call-center-200x300.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="300" srcset="https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/virtual-call-center-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/virtual-call-center.jpg 410w" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" /></a>Call centers are basically centralized offices created for the sake of taking and relaying a huge quantity of calls. A <strong><a title="virtual call center" href="http://www.fusionbposervices.com/">virtual call center</a></strong> is generally run by a specific company for administering incoming service or product supports as well as information requests from the customers. Outgoing phone calls for the purpose of telemarketing and debt collections are also done through such centers. Call centers are also called as contact centers when it collectively handle faxes, letters and email in one single location. Call centers may be divided in two major categories; the inbound call centers and the outbound call centers.</p>
<p>Many businesses, nowadays, are opting for <strong>call center outsourcing.</strong> In fact, this is the latest in trend.  They are adopting this for the sake of their companies. They are using such centers as a platform to interact with their customers round the clock. Companies especially mail order catalogue services, utility services, computer software and hardware normally hire call center services for enhancing customer support service as well growth of their business.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
